24
00:03:12,916 --> 00:03:15,416
<i>Diu Tomboy Genuine Gentleman.</i>

25
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:18,916
<i>Skinny Guitar Skinny, Gaily, and Coolio.</i>

26
