THE AGREEMENT

54
00:05:06,708 --> 00:05:08,458
Let's sign up here.

55
00:05:35,083 --> 00:05:38,083
Hey! Hey there!

56
00:05:38,666 --> 00:05:40,750
You forgot to zip your backpack.

57
00:05:45,416 --> 00:05:46,500
Thank you.

58
00:05:47,250 --> 00:05:48,291
Something wrong!

59
00:05:51,166 --> 00:05:52,458
Is this yours?

60
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:59,916
My Quan!

61
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,000
Who's that girl?

62
00:06:01,666 --> 00:06:04,708
Jeez! He knows her period.

63
