00:53:58,416 --> 00:54:00,216
She even put this on
the school Facebook page.

513
00:54:05,000 --> 00:54:06,166
Hey!

514
00:54:06,250 --> 00:54:07,250
La La Len!

515
00:54:28,500 --> 00:54:29,875
Are you okay?

516
00:54:42,583 --> 00:54:45,541
This brand is good. Bong should use this.

517
00:54:45,625 --> 00:54:48,000
Take care of
your skin for the upcoming Final.

518
00:55:22,750 --> 00:55:23,958
Hey!

519
00:55:24,041 --> 00:55:25,750
Even though baking is for women,

520
00:55:25,833 --> 00:55:28,458
you have to be tougher. Nobody judges.

521
00:55:29,791 --> 00:55:30,958
Tough or soft?

522
00:55:31,458 --> 00:55:33,083
As long as it's beautiful.

523
00:55:34,000 --> 00:55:36,583
When cleaning your suitcase this morning,

524
00:55:36,666 --> 00:55:38,166
I found strange men's underwear.

525
00:55:38,250 --> 00:55:39,916
It isn't yours, is it?

526
00:55:42,041 --> 00:55:46,166
You should get married soon so
that An can have both a mom and a dad.

527
00:55:51,333 --> 00:55:52,625
It looks beautiful.

528
00:55:56,208 --> 00:55:57,750
- Hey!
- Quan!

529
00:55:58,541 --> 00:56:00,000
Let's hang out!

530
00:56:01,750 --> 00:56:04,375
We have a test tomorrow
afternoon. Don't you need to study?

531
00:56:05,125 --> 00:56:06,375
But it's tomorrow afternoon.

532
00:56:08,583 --> 00:56:10,208
An, come shopping with us!

533
00:56:12,416 --> 00:56:13,833
Quan, join us!

534
00:56:13,916 --> 00:56:16,833
Let's go! Go!

535
00:56:16,916 --> 00:56:18,750
Go!

536
00:56:19,250 --> 00:56:20,625
Go! Go!

537
00:56:20,708 --> 00:56:23,666
Your mom called me
from the States the other day,

538
00:56:24,166 --> 00:56:26,458
